  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a clinical trial of CMR guidance for the CRT procedure. Patients will be randomized
      to CMR guidance or standard care for the CRT procedure.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      At baseline, patients will have CMR, echocardiography, and cardiopulmonary exercise testing.
      In patients randomized to CMR guidance for the CRT procedure, LV lead placement will be
      guided by the MRI information related to scar, activation and anatomy. Patients will have
      follow-up assessments at 6 and 12 months.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
